      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：b1是main branch，然后b2和b3都从第一个commit a的位置分出来对吧？b2在上面，b3在下面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b1",
        "b2",
        "b3",
        "commit a"
