    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个结构。然后切到b2做两个commit，id分别是f和g。接着回b1做个commit b。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b2",
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "b1",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，b2现在有f、g两个commit，b1有a、b。接下来b3的部分呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b2",
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "b1",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "切到b3，做commit u和v。然后关键部分来了：b2要merge b1，把b1的最新内容合进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b3",
        "commit u",
        "commit v",
        "b2",
        "merge b1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "b2 merge b1完成。现在b1还要往前走吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b2",
        "b1",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，b1再做个commit c。然后b3 merge b2，之后b3自己再做个commit x。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b1",
        "commit c",
        "b3",
        "merge b2",
        "commit x"
