      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题，你刚才说b3 merge b2，但b2已经merge过b1了，b3现在merge b2会把那些历史都带进来对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b3",
        "b2",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
