    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是要这个效果。然后b2继续做个commit i，接着b3再merge一次b2，b2再merge b1，最后b3再merge b2收尾。",
      "elements_involved": [
